<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1063666" n="1"/>
  <opener><lb/><salute>Viro Consultissimo at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Celeberrimo
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoullio</rs>
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450"></rs><abbr>Jac.</abbr> Hermannus 
    <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute>
    <lb/><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2925535">Ffurti</rs> die <date when="1718-04-29">29 <abbr>Apr.</abbr> 1718</date>.
<lb/></dateline> <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1718-06-07">7. Juni<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></date>.</foreign></note></opener>
<p><lb/>Annus jam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terlapsus est et quod excurrit ex quo <rs type="letter">litteras</rs> Patavio ad me dedisti mihi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
  <lb/>suo tempore reddit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt, et nescio quomodo factum sit ut responsionem in hunc us<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> diem
  <lb/>distulerim. Ante omnia gratulor quod omnia Tibi in insigni statione Tua succedant precor<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
  <lb/>Deum ut Tibi porro tuis<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> laboribus benedicere velit. Postulas a me ut Tibi genium Tuorum
  <lb/>Collegarum notum faciam; quum autem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter Celeberrimos Viros, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11887733X">Polenum</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11757645X">Guilielminum</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119291967">Fardellam</rs>,
  <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118867865">Wallisnerium</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119392364">Ramazzinum</rs> nullum familiariter noverim aliud scribere non possum nisi humanos
  <lb/>doctos<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <add>omnes</add> mihi videri Professores. Ultimis annis accessere Celeberrimus <rs type="person" key="">Lazarinus</rs>, postea ni
  <lb/>fallor <abbr>Cel.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-104265264">Morgagnus</rs> et ultimo <abbr>Rev.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1055630597">Burgos</rs> omnes Eximii Ingenii Viri ex ante nominatis
  <lb/>vero <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-11757645X">Gulielminus</rs> et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119392364">Ramazzinus</rs> mortui sunt et <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119291967">Fardella</rs> <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3172394">Neapoli</rs> ni fallor agit nisi mors eum
  <lb/>etiam eripuerit quod tamen <abbr>D.</abbr> avertat, eum enim omnium familiarissime novi utpote qui octo
  <lb/>mensium spatio in ejus <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus cum eo commoratus sum. Ergo antiquus meus <rs type="person">famulus</rs> et Tibi
  <lb/>nunc servit <rs type="person">Petrus</rs>, ejus fidem sublestam facere non possum nihil<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> contra eundem novi nisi quod
  <lb/>sit bibulus, qua<add>r</add>e nullus dubito quin vina <rs type="place" key="place_KON-italie">Italica</rs> eum <rs type="place" key="/place_GEO-3171728">Patavium</rs> retraxerint; singulis mensibus quinde<pc type="hyphenation"></pc><lb break="no"/>cim libras pro salario accipiebat.</p>
  <p rend="space">Vidisti ergo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="biblio">scriptum</rs> contra me in lucem
  <lb/>protrusum, firmiter proposito meo nihil male morato huic homini respondendi inh<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>reo. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum in <rs type="biblio">Actis
  <lb/><abbr>Lips.</abbr></rs> hujus anni <abbr>Mens.</abbr> <abbr>Apr.</abbr> <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person">Offenburgius</rs> <rs type="biblio">epistolam</rs> hujus fanatici pulchre depexatam dedit, et h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
  <lb/>duo problemata elegantia ipsi vicissim proposuit, <hi rend="u">Invenire <rs type="keyword">Catenariam</rs> data lege <rs type="keyword">virium centralium</rs> ad centr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> finit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>distanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tendentium</hi> et <hi rend="u">Testudinem h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>misph<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ricam fenestris ovalibus perforare quarum periph<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint
  <lb/>absolut<add>e</add><!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren, da vorher <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> stand. --> rectificabiles</hi>.</p>
<p rend="space">Quando dixi Problema inveniendi scalam virium vel temporum alterutra ex hisce datis,
  <lb/>generaliter solvi non posse, fateor mentem meam male expressisse; volui ininuare quod data scala temporum
  <lb/>eo sensu quo in Problemate tuo <rs type="person">Italis</rs> proposito, generaliter inveniri non possit scala virium. <abbr>V. G.</abbr> si scala tempor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
  <lb/>sit <rs type="keyword">hyperbola</rs> dico huic nullam scalam Virium competere posse.</p> <closer>His vale et me ama. 
  <pb facs="1063667" n="2"/>
    
  <address>
    <addrLine>A Monsieur<note type="editorial">Siegel.</note></addrLine>
  <addrLine>Monsieur <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Bernoulli</rs> tres celebre</addrLine>
  <addrLine>Professeur des Mathematiques</addrLine>
  <addrLine>à <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Padoue</rs>.</addrLine>
</address></closer>
